body:
Adds 2-slot, 4-slot, 8-slot, and other multi-slot fluid input/output hatches to [Modern Industrialization](https://modrinth.com/mod/modern-industrialization/).  
为[现代工业化](https://modrinth.com/mod/modern-industrialization/)模组增加2槽、4槽、8槽等多槽流体输入/输出仓。

Allow the same fluid to be output to multiple slots, and allow the same fluid to be input into multiple slots of multi-slot input hatches(these features can be disabled via the configuration file).允许同一流体输出到多个仓室中的多个槽位内,允许同一流体输入到多槽输入仓的多个槽位内（可以通过配置文件禁用）。

Allow direct fluid input and output by right-clicking hatches with fluid containers.允许使用流体容器右键机器仓室直接输入输出流体。

Supports creating multi-slot fluid input/output hatches using [KubeJS](https://modrinth.com/mod/kubejs):  
支持使用[KubeJS](https://modrinth.com/mod/kubejs)创建多槽流体输入输出仓：

```js
// startup_scripts\*.js
MIMachineEvents.registerHatches(event => {
    // Create single-slot fluid input/output hatch
	// 创建单槽流体输入/输出仓
	event.fluid("englishPrefix","prefix","casing",bucketCapacity); 

	// Create multi-slot fluid input/output hatch, total slot count is slotCount
	// 创建多槽流体输入/输出仓，槽位数量为slotCount。
	event.fluid("englishPrefix","prefix","casing",bucketCapacity, slotCount); 

	 // Create multi-slot fluid input/output hatch, with rowSlotCount slots per row and columSlotCount rows
	// 创建多槽流体输入/输出仓，每行有rowSlotCount个槽位，共columSlotCount行。
	event.fluid("englishPrefix","prefix","casing",bucketCapacity, rowSlotCount, columSlotCount); 
})
```

## Requirements 前置需求

- [**Modern Industrialization**](https://modrinth.com/mod/modern-industrialization/versions): 2.4.0+
